King Narnode Shareen is the king of the Tree Gnome Stronghold, part of the Gnome Empire. He is found on the ground floor of the Grand Tree of Tree Gnome Stronghold and features in the following quests:

  • The Grand Tree
  • The Eyes of Glouphrie
  • Monkey Madness I
  • Monkey Madness II

King Narnode is known to have an affection toward humans, but his high regard for the race can often be tainted and contorted through lies, as he once had the player temporarily imprisoned under false accusations.

He is also a customer in the Gnome Restaurant minigame.

Stock[edit | edit source]

After Monkey Madness II is completed, King Narnode sells seed pods through his shop, King Narnode's Royal Seed Pods.
